Class LongArrayIterable

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.markenwerk.commons.iterables.LongArrayIterable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Long>, ProtectedIterable<Long>

    public final class LongArrayIterable
extends Object
implements ProtectedIterable<Long>
    A LongArrayIterable is a ProtectedIterable that generates Iterators that iterate over a given long[].

    1.0.0
